---
<section class="py-20 bg-primary border-y border-primary/80">
  <div class="container-main text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-4">
      Let's build something together
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto">
      Have a project, idea, or opportunity? I'm always open to impactful collaborations.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-11 px-6 rounded-[10px] bg-white text-primary font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-white/90 transition-colors">
        Get in Touch
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="/projects" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-11 px-6 rounded-[10px] border border-white/30 text-white font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
        View Projects
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
